high_descs: Pick up the black glass on the table above the trash can.
Bring the glass to the fridge.
Chill the glass in the fridge for a few seconds.
Bring the glass to the small black table in the corner.
Put the glass on the small black table.
anns.task_desc: Put the glass on the small black table.

high_descs: Go forward until the wall, take right, pick up ice cream cup on  table
take right, walk to middle of room, take right, go to fridge
open fridge, put cup in fridge, close fridge
open fridge, remove cup, take left to table
take right, go to small table
place cup on small table next to counter
anns.task_desc: Cool down the ice cream cup, place next to bowl

high_descs: Walk across the room, then turn right and walk over to the small table in the corner of the room.
Pick up the black blender off of the small table.
Turn right and begin walking across the room, then hang a right and walk up to the fridge.

Open the fridge doors and place the blender into the lower fridge compartment, close the fridge doors and after a couple seconds open the fridge doors again and remove the now chilled blender then close the fridge doors again.
Turn around and take a step forward, then turn right and walk over to the small black shelving unit in between the trash bag and the kitchen counter.
Place the chilled blender onto the top of the black shelving unit in the front left corner.
anns.task_desc: Place a chilled blender onto the top of a black shelving unit.
